
\SNAPSHOT::TOP "Detailed results from the end of the run"


\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS "Dimensions of the grid, number of species, position of separatrix etc."
\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:IMP "Index of the inner midplane"
\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:NATM "Number of atomic species"
\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:NION "Number of test ion species"
