\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:NX "Number of cells in the parallel or poloidal direction"
\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:NY "Number of cells in the radial direction"
\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:OMP "Position of the outer midplane"
\SNAPSHOT::TOP.DIMENSIONS:SEP "Position of the separatrix"
